                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-1120" type="given" value="HANNAH"></interp>HANNAH EDWARDS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of Edward Edwards, and live in Prospect-place, Kentish-town. On the 9th of August, I left my front parlour window a little way open—I hung a blanket en a chair at the foot of the bed, within reach of the window—I missed it, and found it in the policeman's possession.</p>
